OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fdry and warm across the region this
OL,7,Fevening. Perhaps a few patches of low
OL,8,Fcloud in the east but any low cloud
OL,9,Fsoon clearing during the early morning
OL,10,Fto leave clear skies.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FAnother very hot, dry and
OL,13,Fsunny day for most with strong
OL,14,Fsunshine and brisk winds. A chance of
OL,15,Fa few afternoon showers. Windy around
OL,16,Fthe coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
